sources.title: The Misadventures of Mistress Maneater | Full Movie | Action Romance
sources.description:
The Misadventures of Mistress Maneater - With only 30 days to repay a massive loan, a disgraced art historian is forced into a scandalous scheme: win the heart of, and then extort, the Episcopal priest avoiding her like loose glitter. When she discovers him hiding the world's greatest lost masterpiece, will she betray the heroic man who believes in her genius, or fall for him and doom herself to a custom pair of concrete stilettos?
2020. Stars: Lorrisa Julianus, Mickey O'Sullivan, Shannon Brown
